---
title: Easy Honey, Soy & Ginger Pork Meatballs with Ponzu & Celery Slaw
description: Revisit the classic honey-soy duo, but add a signature HelloFresh twist! We've created tender pork meatballs, which
we add to a vibrant and crunchy celery slaw with an extra burst of flavour from ponzu sauce - a Japanese pantry staple with a kick of citrus. Sprinkle over some crushed peanuts and go for your life.
